							</div>
						</div>

						<div style="float: left; width: 33.334%;">
							<div style="margin: 0 10px 0 10px;">
								<span style="font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0 0 -0.6em; position: relative; text-transform: uppercase; z-index: 1;">
